	* configure.ac: Bumped version to 2.0.1.

2004-12-07  Niels Möller  <nisse@lysator.liu.se>

	* Released lsh-2.0.

	* src/environ.h.in (USER_NAME_FROM_ENV): Examine $LOGNAME before
	$USER. This is the same behaviour as emacs and rcs.

