	boundary, raise EXC_FINISH_READ, not EXC_PROTOCOL.

	* src/connection.c (do_exc_connection_handler): Added a comment
	for the EXC_FINISH_READ case.

	* configure.in (BASH): Unset BASH if it has the value "/bin/sh".

