	* src/testsuite/twofish-test.m4: Updated test case to test
	twofish_cbc. 

	* src/testsuite/des-test.m4: Updated test case to test des3_cbc.

	* src/idea.c: Deleted file.

	* src/des.c, src/twofish.c: Deleted files, replaced by code in
	crypto.c. 

